name: Swoosh Token
description: Millions of people enjoy watching others realize creative ideas. Be it in the gaming sector or in other artistic activities that take place online. Swoosh connects content creators and their supporters by bringing them even closer together. The core feature of Swoosh is the communication between creators and their supporters through crypto donations, which can include personal messages. Creators have the possibility to reply to those messages, engage into a chat with their supporters and take the relationship to the next level.
